  <dsc><c01 id="aspace_ea5d4c6aacfb8a5816bbbffda271da40" level="file"><did><unittitle>Periodicals and news clippings</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1979/1979">1979</unitdate><unitdate normal="1984/1992" type="inclusive">1984-1992</unitdate><container id="aspace_325f4552d49369dcc898e5d17ec4bf01" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_a18856c67987518848e559e922c9cbfe" parent="aspace_325f4552d49369dcc898e5d17ec4bf01" type="folder">1</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_46a41258357d2dae29d06ca6db632e71"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes debate over gay priests, potential cause of AIDS identified.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_a28f7faa1d58b96d1359f367dc6e5104" level="file"><did><unittitle>Promotional materials</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1987/1991" type="inclusive">1987-1991</unitdate><unitdate normal="1994/1994">1994</unitdate><container id="aspace_9408fd31d8de2e9c9881a88de77303da" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_0e1b5486cd07a0f96f3573d0d37b2866" parent="aspace_9408fd31d8de2e9c9881a88de77303da" type="folder">2</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_e4659220f8c2aa2c0b247e6d587d6998"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Fliers, pamphlets, programs, invitations for conventions, events, resorts in and around Rochester.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_33d896b8ae762019aef74f6b03c58294" level="file"><did><unittitle>"Is the Church Today a Dysfunctional Family?: A Pastoral Letter from Matthew Fox to Cardinal Ratzinger"</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1988-08-08/1988-08-08">August 8, 1988</unitdate><container id="aspace_e501aa0c95b3c0f7935a7ae0fa89711c" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_6cd78b41e7bcb1844c352f8255d67487" parent="aspace_e501aa0c95b3c0f7935a7ae0fa89711c" type="folder">3</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_a802fde11fdd9bb448b83453c7c1e750"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>An article of a letter from Matthew Fox, O.P., writing to Cardinal Ratzinger and the whole Church, defending his work against Ratzinger's criticisms that it is unorthodox, dangerous, and deviant.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_9738d5a12a087b5bfc68a58515569a46" level="file"><did><unittitle>Bias-Related Violence Bill- Debate Transcript</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1990-09-13/1990-09-13">September 13, 1990</unitdate><container id="aspace_423b05a560bd1aa9d209d5269aeaa165" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_b5f8e6948f4487c729baef70d2e6ba9e" parent="aspace_423b05a560bd1aa9d209d5269aeaa165" type="folder">4</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_d043d77309cf254a79f5abf8b0f61e56" level="file"><did><unittitle>Letter from the Diocese of Rochester</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1997-03-13/1997-03-13">March 13, 1997</unitdate><container id="aspace_54423d7f4a694c4bc51ad8c37b7ffa7a" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_9a1521ade151d8b41ec51e8cea36cc99" parent="aspace_54423d7f4a694c4bc51ad8c37b7ffa7a" type="folder">5</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_b9f6021978790c9ad3e79df1a1a7a331"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Letter from Matthew Clark, Bishop of Rochester, thanking Mary McCrank for her support of their celebration for gay and lesbian Catholics.</p></scopecontent></c01></dsc>
